By saying I had a  pack of 50's, wasnt to say I'm right your wrong, it was to say I'm not a noob who picked up the game and someone played a cruel joke on. <br>
<br>
Taking away speccable shield removes guard and more importantly engage. How many mercs have engage?<br>
<br>
Being able to dw and use a shield can be a power full tool. A firby on your cleric? Shield whips out that is guarding cleric, slam, back to dw and kill. Pesky caster? Jimb breaks bubble, slam, dw to death. Zerker gerbils on you? Slam, dw and repeat. Caster or healer taken to much agro in pve? It has many valuable uses.<br>
<br>
